args: The group set off in search of materials for\nZardin's cosmetics. But when they arrived\nat their destination, they found fiends waiting.
I wish we'd known this was a fiends' nest\nbefore we got here!
Live and learn, boss.\nLet's just take 'em out!

Let us finish this before my fringe becomes
disheveled. Ah, I see I am as beautiful in
the mirror today as ever. 
Hiyah!
Hm? What was that ugly sound?
It came from the fiend, no?\n...Hey! This fiend seems to have fainted!
Hey, yer right! It wasn't a fatal wound,\nbut it's out cold.
What does it matter?\nMy FRINGE, Ranzal.
Let us finish this at once! Hiyah!
Are you using some sort of new\ntechnique, Zardin?
It's business as usual on my end.\nAll I've done differently is spend\na touch more time on my makeup.
Wait, it couldn't be...\nLet me try something.
That looks like their leader!\nWe can talk later, let's—
What?! Even the BOSS fainted?!\nThe hell's goin' on here?
Ha ha! There is a simple solution, friends.
The answer is the same as it is with\nall things: beauty. I am simply too\nbeautiful!
I surmise that my beauty is robbing\nthese fiends of their very consciousness.
As you saw, I merely gave their leader\na tender tap, and he fell belly up.
I mean, yeah, we all saw that, but...\nNo way, that's bullplop!
Maybe beauty is more powerful than\nI thought...
Don't go buyin' into his nonsense,\n{player_name}!
It's no surprise one as beautiful as\nyourself can see the truth.
There truly is no end to what\nI can achieve with my beauty!
In fact, I wager I've barely scratched\nthe surface.
I shall continue bringing out the beauty\nin others, that I might discover even\nmore of my potential!
Oh, how I long to witness my future glory!
Ah, but what if I should become TOO\nbeautiful? What dangers might I incur?

What if the entire continent—and
even nature itself—became so
jealous of my beauty that it
ceased all function to chase it...
...leading to the collapse of civilization,\nand the world becoming a frozen,\nuninhabitable wasteland!
But on the other hand, I might become\nso beautiful I can perform miracles...
Like mending an entire village in\na single night!
Come on, now you're just bein'\nsilly. Somethin' like that'd even\nstun the Goddess herself!
Perhaps my beauty could cause changes\nin those around me as well...
Suddenly, even nearby fiends might\nbecome beautiful!
That would be pretty great.\nCleo and Elisanne would be overjoyed.
Ideas abound! The potential of my\nbeauty is truly staggering.
Just imagining my own fairness\nis enough to stop my heart!
I feel your belief. Look—my face\nhas grown eighty percent more\nbeautiful in response!
Now that I better understand my potential,\nI must set to work on increasing my\nbeauty still!
Come, let us gather these herbs and\nreturn to the castle posthaste!\nThere is much to do!
Oh, but you are SO beautiful!
Hey, wait up! We don't even know which\nherbs we're lookin' for!
Yeesh... Guy's away with the faeries.
Ha ha, nothing wrong with that.\nBy the way...
Do you really think he could make\nfiends cuter?
Are you—come ON, dude!\nHow gullible can ya be?!
Although... If he DOES manage to pull\nthat off, he'd be pretty special.\n...I'm kinda curious now...
